{"timestamp": "2025-12-03 09:05:04.938687", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission completed successfully.\n\nSummary of submitted solution:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"pc_0_1\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"host_incorrect_ip\", \"host_incorrect_gateway\", \"host_ip_conflict\"]\n\nDiagnosis recap and recommended fix (for operator use):\n- pc_0_1 is configured with IP 10.0.0.2/24 and gateway 10.0.0.1 but is physically attached to the 10.0.1.0/24 leaf (leaf_router_0_1).\n- This created a duplicate IP with pc_0_0 and caused packets from pc_0_1 to be sent to the wrong leaf and fail ARP resolution.\n- Fix: Reconfigure pc_0_1 with an IP in the 10.0.1.0/24 subnet (for example 10.0.1.2/24) and set its default gateway to 10.0.1.1 (leaf_router_0_1). Then verify unique IPs and successful ARP/gateway resolution and rerun reachability tests.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2242, "output_tokens": 234, "total_tokens": 2476, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
